---

🔹 Important Properties (Basics)

1. Log of 1

logₐ(1) = 0

Because

a⁰ = 1

Example:

log₇(1) = 0


---

2. Log of Base

logₐ(a) = 1

Example:

log₅(5) = 1


---

3. Log of a Power

logₐ(aⁿ) = n

Example:

log₂(2⁶)

= 6


